        <updateDate>2003-08-12T20:16:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Public Safety Officers Flag Act - Directs: (1) the Secretary of Homeland Security to furnish a flag to drape the casket of each public safety officer killed in the line of duty; and (2) the flag to be given to the officer's next of kin after the burial.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
